data.description: This turn key home is ready for a new owner! Renovated top to bottom, there is lots of NEW inside and out to love here! Offering 3 Bedrooms and 1.75 baths; a large eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops - a walk-in pantry with a deep freezer that stays!; spacious rooms, 3 heat sources - including dually zoned Heat Pump with Central Air and a coal stove if you want to be extra cozy on those cold winter nights! 1st floor 3/4 bath and second floor laundry! The back deck offers a great place to enjoy, overlooking the large fenced in yard with above ground swimming pool and firepit area. Need storage? This comes with a shed and room for 6 cars to park! Don't delay, call today! Agents: This is a 10G property!
